WEBVTT

00:05:29.448 --> 00:05:31.862
This is an OXO potato peeler.

00:05:31.886 --> 00:05:35.508
It was originally designed
for people with arthritis,

00:05:35.532 --> 00:05:37.959
but it was so comfortable,
everybody loved it.

00:05:39.792 --> 00:05:44.198
Text messaging: that was originally
designed for people who are Deaf.

00:05:44.817 --> 00:05:47.067
And as you know,
everybody loves that, too.

00:05:47.091 --> 00:05:49.009
(Laughter)

00:05:49.033 --> 00:05:50.746
I started thinking:

00:05:51.492 --> 00:05:54.618
What if we changed our mindset?

00:05:55.578 --> 00:06:00.706
What if we started designing
for disability first --